description: This was a crazy day. Sun was shining so I went out looking for another outdoor action. I met a young couple on their trip to Prague. The boy was super hot so I tried my luck even with his girlfriend around. To my surprise and amusement, she actually helped me a lot in my quest. The guy was shy but she literally made him to do the stuff I wanted because she was after my money. The poor boy was in love with her so he did all she told him to do. He wasn´t happy about it, maybe he was even angry at that greedy skank. Don´t worry, when the things got serious, I sent her away. I wanted the boy only for myself. Too bad there were so many people around... In pure desperation, we went deep into reeds and nettles that grew nearby. That tight little ass was worth it.
title: Czech Hunter 309
